title: dallas 11x27 Top Gun.avi
description:
YES boys and girls, it is finally here:
DALLAS season 11 brings you another 30 great episodes of the Ewing saga.


Cliff's drug addiction worsens; J.R. eagerly prepares to run Weststar, not aware of the surprise that awaits him; Bobby feels Kay's career is more important to her than he; Laurel tells Clayton about the blackmail scheme.

original air date : Friday April 8, 1988

Priscilla Presley (Jenna) is not present in this episode. 

The episode title is borrowed from the 1986 film, Top Gun.
